acquire_methods.description: The Pig's Foot is obtained by beating Guber in a race on The End island.
The Wolf Paw is obtained by completing the Woods Race in 32 seconds or less, then talking to Gustave.
To get Frozen Chicken, you need to beat the 3rd Checkpoint of the Chicken Race.
Upon completing the main Harp songs (excluding the Personal Harp songs, Through the Campfire and Pachelbel) with a 100% score, Melody will reward you with a strand of her hair.
It is obtained through the Dungeon Hub by completing 4/4 of any of the Dungeon Races. Races can be started by talking to Guildford next to the start race pad.
The King Talisman is obtained after speaking to all seven kings while they are the active king.
Bingo Talisman can be bought from the Bingo Shop for 100 Bingo Points, once the player has reached  Bingo Rank I (1).
